text: Nieszawa is a town in Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship, north-central Poland. *Statutes of Nieszawa, enacted in 1454 Nieszawa may also refer to the following villages: *Nieszawa, Lublin Voivodeship (east Poland) *Nieszawa, Greater Poland Voivodeship (west-central Poland)
title: Nieszawa (disambiguation)
